        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "@clason happy to ask upstream in tree-sitter, but at least from their own JSONSchema, the [grammar name is fine with hyphens](https://github.com/tree-sitter/tree-sitter/blob/495b069667fd3d4cadb18bf812468264a102c877/docs/src/assets/schemas/config.schema.json#L13-L17), which just came from https://github.com/tree-sitter/tree-sitter/pull/5315. (The [related discussion](https://github.com/tree-sitter/tree-sitter/discussions/5321) seems to want to avoid `-` in grammar names, but it seems like that ship has sailed...?)",
